#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/__init__.py:docstring
#: of numpy.polyadd:22
msgid ""
"The sum of the inputs. If either input is a poly1d object, then the output "
"is also a poly1d object. Otherwise, it is a 1D array of polynomial "
"coefficients from highest to lowest degree."
